GENERAL
=======

- CopyRight are not up-to-date.

- Move all bitmaps to
  ~beta/bitmap/bifrost and
  ~beta/bitmap/mjolner.

- Find all occurrences of "error!" and try if the compiler can handle them.

- Maybe problem with first event in sequence under motif.

- Two refresh events at opening of window under guienv?

- Implement IntegerList (if needed)

- Implement all patterns marked with "(* Not Yet Implemented *)" or that
  calls the pattern UnImplemented.

- Use ObjectPool for PathHandler
   
- In readpbmfile: Furtherbind binary::<trueobject if RAWBITS.
  However, since whitespace is ignored, it is probably not needed.

- Opgrade the animation package.

- replace all TOS calls.

- InteractionHandler should look more like eventhandler
  (doubleclick and event names are not the same).

- Hardspace in source files confuses BETA-parser (e.g. in macintosh files).
  Compiler should print these as e.g. \017 in lst file.

- 0->PutPixel is not implemented under X11 (i.e. resetting of
  a pixel).

- initCanvas: check that fonts are initialized.

- Maybe there are too many operations on Canvas, now that it 
  inherits from guienv.Canvas? E.g. Map/Unmap.

- Add PredefinedGraphicalObject RoundRect.
  X11 implementation can be done using a Public Domain X11 extension.

- WriteEPS: add parameters "fit", "border", "margin".

- Use the copy operation suggested in the BETA FAQ instead of the 
  current implementation.

- X11 impl: Maybe allocate own collormap, to prevent
  color allocation from failing.
  E.g. demo/colorscale on some servers.

- INCLUDE of guienv_unixprivte in BifrostX11impl should
  NOT be needed because of the include of callbacks.
  Compiler error?



BDRAW
=====

- Cut, Clear, Delete does not work.

- Jeg har bemærket en underlig opførsel i bdraw:
  Prøv at tegne en ellipse i bdraw;
  Tryk derefter en enkelt gang på et af hjørnerne;
  Og vupti: ellipsen er skrumpet til micro størrelse.
  Jeg har ikke selv gjort noget for at kigge efter hvor fejlen ligger.
  Jeg er derfor ikke helt sikker på om det bare er en fejl i bdraw,
  eller om det er en fejl i Bifrost. 
  /Peter Ahe

- Group/ungroup virker ikke

- Implementer smoothness

- dialoger ikke f{rdiggjort under guienv.

- Duplicate: If two objects selected, and Duplicate is performed,
  one of the two new objects will be highlighted wrong.

- Immediate paste puts the new object into position (0,0).

- Cut+Copy: Update clipboard (if visible)

- Update menus when selection changes (enable/disable items)

- Initial title should be "bdraw: Untitled"
  (only relevant after save has been implemented)

- Add extensions.pagesize: @rectangle

- bdraw native print (non-postscript) fails in Windows implementation

